%% 3. Sequence: Load Forecasts for Selected City
sequenceDiagram
 autonumber
 participant U as User
 participant UI as Angular Component(s)
 participant S as WeatherApiService
 participant C as WeatherController
 participant B as WeatherService
 participant D as SQLite (Dapper)

 U->>UI: Select City
 UI->>S: getForecasts(cityId)
 S->>C: GET /api/weather?cityId=#
 C->>B: GetForecasts(cityId)
 B->>D: SELECT * FROM Forecast WHERE CityId=#
 D-->>B: Rows
 B-->>C: Forecast DTO list
 C-->>S: 200 OK (JSON)
 S-->>UI: Promise resolve (data)
 UI->>UI: Update signals / computed
 UI-->>U: Render table